               <msContents>
                  <summary>On the meaning of Aẓe and Ǧanhoy, Palace Etiquette at Susənyos’s Court, On the Christological Controversy, List of the first forty abbots of Däbrä Libanos,
                    Lamentations of the Virgin, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰቆቃወ፡ ድንግል፡</foreign>, Image of Mary of Qwəsqwam, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መልክዐ፡ ቍስቋም፡</foreign>
                  </summary>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="3r"/>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                     <title>On the meaning of <foreign xml:lang="gez">አፄ፡</foreign> and <foreign xml:lang="amh">ጃንሆይ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                       በስመ፡ አብ፡...ንዌጥን፡ ታሪከ፡ ነገሥት፡ ብሂል፡ አፄ፡ ስመ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ተወጥነ፡ በትግሬ፡...
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from="3r" to="6r"/>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                    <title>Palace Etiquette at <name ref="PRS9038Susenyos"/>&gt; Court.</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        <locus target="#3r"/>
                      ወአመ፡ ይገብር፡ ፍትሐ፡ ወይትማከር፡ ምክረ፡ ሱስንዮስ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ይነብር፡ ዲበ፡ መንበሩ፡...<locus target="#5r"/>ወአመ፡ የሐውር፡ ንጉሥ፡ በጉዞ፡...
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                    <locus from="6r" to="20r"/>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                    <title>On the Christological controversies of the Gonderite era.</title>
                    <note>I. Guidi, “Di due frammenti relativi alla storia di Abissinia,” Rendiconti della Accademia Nazionale dei Lincei. Classe di scienze morali . . ., vol. 2 (1893), pp. 596–605.</note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                    <locus from="20v"/>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                    <title>List of the first forty abbots of <foreign xml:lang="gez">ደብረ፡ ሊባኖስ፡</foreign>, from <name ref="PRS9150TaklaHa"/> to <name ref="PRS9272TasfaGi"/> of Wəddo.</title>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                    <locus from="21r" to="34r"/>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                    <title>Lamentations of the Virgin, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰቆቃው፡ ድንግል፡</foreign></title>
                    <note>P. Chrysostome Hayoz, Portrait de la Vierge. Complainte de la Vierge, Fribourg (Switzerland), 1956; Chaîne, Répertoire, no. 268. MG 59</note>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ እግ"፡ ሥሉስ፡ ሕፀተ፡ ግጻዌ፡ ዘአልቦ። ሰቆቃወ፡ ድንግል፡ እጽሕፍ፡ በቀለመ፡ አንብዕ፡ ወአንጠንጥቦ።</incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                    <locus from="34r" to="37r"/>
                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT1862Malkea"/>
                    <note>Chaîne, Répertoire, no. 175.</note>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምኪ፡ በመጽሐፈ፡ ሕይወት፡ ልኩዕ። ወለስእርተ፡ ርእስኪ፡ ጸሊም፡ ከመ፡ ኅብረ፡ ቋዕ። ፈለስተ፡ ቍስቋም፡ ማርያም፡ ተስፋ፡ ፈላስያን፡ ሰብእ።</incipit>

                  </msItem>

               </msContents>
